criteria.driver_alignment:
Discover — documented and justified initial real estate/construction and working-capital assumptions and gave sources (comps to Seattle/Shanghai/NYC) and conservative choices;  
Represent/Implement — translated assumptions into explicit modeling choices (depreciation, salvage, rent, tax shield) and implemented them in code;  
Validate — stress-tested cost/revenue/WACC assumptions via sensitivity analysis confirming robustness;  
Reflect — interpreted implications and conservatism of the assumptions.
